data.description: Seller is offering $5,000 seller's concession for closing costs! POOL HOME! 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom, plus Den/Flex room with an oversized 1 car garage available now in the NO HOA neighborhood of Deer Park! This house has a lot of character ranging from the real oak floors to the pristine and private swimming pool and the wood beamed cathedral ceilings. This home has the perfect kitchen for entertaining your guests with two islands and lots of counter space and cabinetry. The pool has the capability to make it the right temperature for your choosing as well as a tastefully installed pool cover. The home is perfect for all the family gatherings with 1,570 sqft inside and the nicely sized pool/patio area to host! No hassle from an HOA because there isn't one in this neighborhood so you can park your cars, RV's, and other toys on your property! The school district is very sought after with it being River Ridge Middle and High School and the house is tucked away in the neighborhood that is centrally located to everything you will need as well as the major highways to get you to places quickly but without being near the hustle and bustle.
